Rating: 2
This is a good basic bulgur pilaf recipe. Next time I would toast the pine nuts (or sliced almonds) in a dry skillet and saute the onion in just 1 - 2 T oil.

Rating: 3
This dish is yummy both ways, but the individual flavors come out more at room temperature, and so that's my preference. I think it'd be great with the addition of a little bit of fresh mint.

