This is sooo yummy I acutally like it better cold than heated. It is addictive!

Rating: 2
Tasty, even as a light dinner on its own or even as a cold lunch. Kind of tastes like it's missing something that I can't quite put my finger on.

Rating: 3
I made this for Thanksgiving this year (2005). Everyone seemed to like it; they mentioned especially the toasted pine nuts as being a feature. The apricots I used were the California variety, as recommended. I thought they were too dry and tart. Next time I think I will try the plumper, moister dried apricots. The ones that looked that way in the market were the Mediterranean variety.